2.1
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Newton's First Law states that an object at rest stays at rest.

2.2
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:45.000
And an object in motion stays in motion unless acted upon by a net force.

2.3
00:00:45.000 --> 00:01:00.000
This behavior is called inertia.

