When I hit the puck, it moves forward, demonstrating the change in motion.

3.3
00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:45.000
This shows how inertia works in real life.

4.1
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:52.500
In summary, inertia keeps objects in their state of motion.

4.2
00:01:52.500 --> 00:02:00.000
Understanding this principle helps us analyze movement in sports and beyond.

